_header: For foul lusts I have withstood
_description: Dialogue between the Saved and the Damned — four couplets

BLHar7322.First Lines: For foule lustes I witstodIn blisse I were ȝis garlond…
BLHar7322.Last Lines: …In heuene blisse I am in helefor I forsok ȝys worldes wele
BLHar7322.Note: Set out as verse lines though inserted in a Latin text, with Latin prose text continuing in narrow column to right.
